items.title: Banjo-Kazooie Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Banjo-Kazooie Wiki!
items.desc:
Welcome to the wiki all about the Banjo-Kazooie series of video games, covering the backstory, characters, enemies, bosses, locations, items an dobjects, abilities, transformations, mini-games, secrets, music and much more!

The Banjo-Kazooie series is a set of video games developed by the UK-based company Rare, Ltd. The first game, Banjo-Kazooie, debuted in 1998 for the Nintendo 64. A sequel was made in 2000 for the same system titled Banjo-Tooie.

In 2003, an inter-sequel that takes place between the first two games, Banjo-Kazooie: Grunty's Revenge, was released for the Game Boy Advance, and in 2005 a spin-off racing game, Banjo-Pilot, was also made for the Game Boy Advance. Two ports of Grunty's Revenge, called Banjo-Kazooie: Grunty's Revenge Mobile and Banjo-Kazooie: Grunty's Revenge Missions, were later made available in 2004 and 2005 as applications for download on cell phones.

Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts and Bolts, was released in November of 2008. To celebrate this release, Microsoft and Rare also released updated versions of the original Banjo-Kazooie in December 2008 and Banjo-Tooie in April 2009, both of which are currently available for download on Xbox Live Arcade.

items.headline: Welcome to the Zoo Tycoon Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to the Zoo Tycoon Wiki, the community site about Zoo Tycoon that anyone can edit, including you! This is the largest Zoo Tycoon fan site and resource on the web, containing articles on the latest games, animals, and an up-to-date record of the fan community. If you want to share your knowledge and passion with your fellow fans, join us today!

items.headline: Welcome to the Tiny Zoo Wiki
items.desc:
This is a wiki about the iOS / Android app Tiny Zoo Friends by TinyCo, Inc.

Tiny Zoo is an great game where you can build your dream zoo! Breed your exotic animals, decorate your little zoo, and have endless fun while doing so! This is a free app but you can spend money as you progress through the game.
